reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Definitely has done its job!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this 3 pack screen protector for mine and my kids phones, I have used this brand before and loved it so I decided to stick with what I know. Glad I did cause everything about these is exceptional. It's so easy to install on to the phones I was able to even do it myself, not a bubble in sight crystal clear image. All the buttons work nicely and it has held up to be a great protector so far seeing as how I drop my phone too many times to even count. My son plays with my phone and I now can confidently hand it over with no fear. My favorite part is that it comes with 3 and a bonus is the camera lens protectors also, definitely a necessity for sure. They did not disappoint!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Very affordable and you get 3 protectors which you can’t beat! It fits the 14 pro screen perfectly and it feels protective. What impressed me the most was the little camera protectors- I had planned on throwing them away but then I got the phone and realized that the lenses are huge and they stick out a lot so these little protectors are a necessity with this phone. It was super easy to install, no bubbles or anything.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Could get 5 Stars....
reviews.reviewText: Pros:- Low Cost, Low Cost, Low Cost... did I mention the low cost?- Same quality as the more expensive protectors- Easy Installation- Plenty of extra wipes- Instructions are printed on the internal side of the box so you never lose themCons:- No wet wipes even though the wipes are marked as Wet and Dry. Not a big deal but...I would have given it 5 stars, but the wet wipes are missing so I took 1 star off. Otherwise, this is a great product and for the price of $5 and change it's a no brainer.

reviews.reviewText: The glass was easy to install. No problems and it fit well the phone.The camera cover was easy to install to, it fits well, and gives the finishing look I think apple missed. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 12, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome for the $ and smooth!
reviews.reviewText: I am very picky when it comes to phone accessories, but I am very happy with my purchase. Its not perfect be it still beat my expectation. First the bad, the rear camera cover I am not impressed with. It adds quite a bit of bulk, will smudge easily with fingerprints and after a week already has a small scratch. But is see this as a bonus item and will give it a shot to see how it fairs long term. For the good, the main screen protector is easy to install, has plenty of wet and dry wipes as well as dust removal stickers for installation. Unlike most screen protectors I have tried this glass feels amazingly smooth and is very fingerprint resistant. It is not a full edge to edge protection which leaves a small gap since I use a very slim case. For people with larger cases this will be beneficial to reduce any interference.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Camera lens cover cracked for no reason
reviews.reviewText: Very easy to install. No bubbles or anything. Super quick and you just can’t make a mistake. The issue I have is with the cover for the camera lenses. All I did was slide my phone across the table and part of it just completely shattered into little tiny bits, I’ve never damaged a phone in anyway whatsoever in my entire life and I’ve had cell phones since back in the day when you had to carry a big kiss around with you when you’re paid five dollars a minute. Not happy with this product. It was less expensive than others but I certainly didn’t expect it to shatter in a week. Pretty bummed.
